technicalDescription:
Affect the display of an already created order on the kitchen monitor.

Credit is given for one of the following:
- deleting the order from the kitchen monitor;
- changing the order contents;
- changing item quantities;
- adding or removing items;
- changing the comment, order number, status, or other displayed data;
- changing order routing, including sending the order to a non‑existent kitchen monitor.

There will be one kitchen monitor in the environment, but if the participant can change the route and send the order to a non‑existent kitchen monitor, this is accepted.

The focus is on the result seen on the kitchen monitor.
